title: The Sims 2 Bon Voyage
description:
Game information:

=================



- Travel to Three Dream Destinations

- Stay at Hotels or Vacation Homes

- Enjoy All-New Activities, Cultures, & Tours

- Buy & Discover Unique Items



- Requires The Sims 2, The Sims 2 Special DVD Edition, The Sims 2 Holiday

Edition, or The Sims 2 Deluxe for PC to play.



Installation Information:

=========================



Just extract the archives and burn/mount with your favorite software.

Install, when asked for serial enter: XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX

Copy our crack from DVD to game dir overwriting the old then play.
